<strong>Current and future projects</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Statistical learning applied to microbial dynamics (Bayesian nonparametrics, layered latent state-space models)</li>
  <li>Theoretical foundations at the intersection of machine learning and control</li>
  <li>Genetically engineering and controlling a microbial consortia</li>
  <li>Host-Microbiome interactions</li>
  <li>Time series metagenomics</li>
</ul>

