<h2 id="our-experimental-biology-research">Our experimental biology research</h2>
<p>Our main experimental system is gnotobiotic mice (germ-free), where we can colonize mice with whatever background flora we desire.</p>

<figure class="image">
<img src="/image/mouse_time.png" alt="mouse time series" style="width: 650px;
